  1→     1→/**
  2→     2→ * CrowdStrike Vulnerability Lookup Component
  3→     3→ *
  4→     4→ * Enables real-time querying of CrowdStrike Falcon API for system vulnerabilities
  5→     5→ *
  6→     6→ * Features:
  7→     7→ * - Search form with hostname or AWS instance ID input (Feature 041)
  8→     8→ * - Auto-detection of input type (hostname vs instance ID)
  9→     9→ * - Results table matching CurrentVulnerabilitiesTable design
 10→    10→ * - Filter by severity, exception status, product
 11→    11→ * - Sortable columns
 12→    12→ * - Save to database functionality
 13→    13→ * - Loading and error states
 14→    14→ *
 15→    15→ * Related to:
 16→    16→ * - Feature 015-we-have-currently (CrowdStrike System Vulnerability Lookup)
 17→    17→ * - Feature 041-falcon-instance-lookup (AWS Instance ID Support)
 18→    18→ * Tasks: T031-T036 [US1-Impl], T055-T058 [US3-Impl], T025-T029 [US2-Impl]
 19→    19→ */
 20→    20→
